{
    "name": "Giant Dragonfly",
    "type": "creature",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Giant Dragonfly",
            "type": "section",
            "text": "These buzzing insects are the size of a small horse. They're ambush predators that hunt beasts and humanoids alike, capable of using impressive aerial acrobatics to swoop down from above and snatch away their prey.",
